				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The {{gtClass:GtEnsembleBoardSnippet}} embeds a kanban board inline in a Lepiter page. A single snippet class supports three modes via two parameters (`boardType` and `projectName`):"
